title: Active Oil Pipelines in the Gulf of Mexico, World, 2008
name: Active Oil Pipelines in the Gulf of Mexico, World, 2008
description: This data set displays the active pipeline in the Gulf of Mexico. These pipelines are used to transport natural resources from the off shore wells/platforms. This data has been taken from the master pipeline data sets provided by the MMS which include all existing pipelines in the MMS database.
